      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor just says \"keep doing what you're doing\" and doesn't really listen to how much this is affecting my quality of life. if i were to go really heavy on the garlic and maybe some ginger too, wouldn't those have a similar effect on blood flow since they are natural blood thinners? i feel like i should at least be able to manage it myself with supplements while i wait for my next appointment.",
